title: Morning Joe 2/15/21
description: The Senate on Saturday voted to acquit former President Donald Trump on a charge of incitement of insurrection despite significant Republican support for conviction. The Morning Joe panel discusses the 57 to 43 vote.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
